{"id": "art-375", "label": "Art. 375", "title": "Art. 375: Procedura în cazul recunoaşterii învinuirii", "slug": "art-375", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_463338995\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1757\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_463338995\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 375:\nProcedura în cazul recunoa&#351;terii învinuirii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1614652286\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1756\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1614652286\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; inculpatul solicit&#259; ca judecata s&#259;\naib&#259; loc în condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 374 alin. (4),\ninstan&#355;a procedeaz&#259; la ascultarea acestuia, dup&#259; care, luând\nconcluziile procurorului &#351;i ale celorlalte p&#259;r&#355;i, se\npronun&#355;&#259; asupra cererii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1773875380\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1755\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1773875380\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)Inculpatul poate recunoa&#351;te faptele\n&#351;i solicita judecarea cauzei în condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 374\nalin. (4) &#351;i prin înscris autentic.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_388574652\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1754\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_388574652\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>2</sup>)În cazurile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1)\n&#351;i (1<sup>1</sup>), dac&#259; inculpatul este minor, este necesar&#259;\n&#351;i încuviin&#355;area reprezentantului s&#259;u legal.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_496842065\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1753\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_496842065\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; admite cererea, instan&#355;a întreab&#259;\np&#259;r&#355;ile &#351;i persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259; dac&#259; propun\nadministrarea de probe cu înscrisuri.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1870930164\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1752\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1870930164\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; respinge cererea, instan&#355;a\nprocedeaz&#259; potrivit art. 374 alin. (5)-(12).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}